\pard\par
\pard Pitfalls:\par
\pard\li720\fi-360 \bullet\tab Redundancy: student details, plan details, and menu details are repeated in many rows.\par
\pard\li720\fi-360 \bullet\tab Update anomaly: if the room number or plan type changes, it must be updated in multiple tuples.\par
\pard\li720\fi-360 \bullet\tab Insertion anomaly: a new student or a new menu cannot be inserted independently without mixing unrelated data.\par
\pard\li720\fi-360 \bullet\tab Deletion anomaly: deleting one attendance or feedback record may also remove useful student or menu information from the same row.\par
\pard\li720\fi-360 \bullet\tab Poor scalability: combining menu, attendance, feedback, and staff details into one table makes querying and maintenance difficult.\par
