\pard\li720\fi-360 \bullet\tab (student_id, attendance_date, meal_type) -> attendance_status\par
\pard\li720\fi-360 \bullet\tab student_id ->> feedback_rating, feedback_comments (multiple feedback entries over time in an unnormalized view)\par
